org.fxyz3d.shapes.containers

Interface ShapeContainerBase<T extends javafx.scene.shape.MeshView>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the primitiveMeshClass this container implements
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Capsule, Cone, ShapeContainer, Spheroid, Torus

    public interface ShapeContainerBase<T extends javafx.scene.shape.MeshView>
    Basic Group for holding FX(yz) primitive MeshViews Allows for selfIllumination and emissiveLighting. Lazily implemented Transforms: Rotate(x,y,z), Translate, Scale.
